EmailTemplate.subject: Webinar Reminder: Optimize TCAS Troubleshooting

<[[https://aerospace.honeywell.com/]]> Tech Tips Webinar: Optimize TCAS Troubleshooting Thank you for registering... Date February 22, 2018
Time 11am-12pm EST (UTC -5)
Location Free Webinar - Register and Attend <[[https://honeywell.webcasts.com/starthere.jsp?ei=1181327&tp_key=d318927d83]]>
Thank you for registering for our Tech Tips webinar exploring Honeywell traffic alert collision avoidance system (TCAS) technical troubleshooting.
Please join Mark Liles, a Honeywell product support expert, to explore maintenance best practices and published technical service information to optimize TCAS troubleshooting and reduce no-fault-founds. Attend here <[[https://honeywell.webcasts.com/starthere.jsp?ei=1181327&tp_key=d318927d83]]>.
Questions will be answered and a recording will be available on MyAerospace after the event.
CLICK HERE TO ATTEND <[[https://honeywell.webcasts.com/starthere.jsp?ei=1181327&tp_key=d318927d83]]>
